msgid "Quire"
msgstr "Quire"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.desktop.in:3
#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:8
msgid "Combine and edit PDF files"
msgstr "Kombineeri ja muuda PDF-faile"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.desktop.in:9
msgid "PDF;Merge;Split;Extract;Organize;Watermark;"
msgstr ""
"PDF;Merge;Split;Extract;Organize;Watermark;liitmine;mestimine;tükeldamine;eraldamine;haldamine;haldus;metateave;metainfo;vesimärk;vesimärgid;"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:10
msgid ""
"Quire is a simple GNOME utility for working with local PDF files without a "
"complex document suite."
msgstr ""
"Quire on lihtne GNOME'i tarvik, mis aitab teha lihtsamaid toiminguid "
"kohalike PDF-failidega ilma keeruka tarkvara kasutamiseta."

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:11
msgid ""
"Merge multiple PDFs, organize pages, extract page ranges, split documents, "
"compress files, and edit metadata without sending them to an online service."
msgstr ""
"Mesti mitu PDF-faili üheks, halda lehti, jaga dokumente tükkideks, paki "
"faile kokku ja muuda metateavet ilma neid edastamata võrguteenusele."

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:15
msgid "Francisco Vásquez Cuevas"
msgstr "Francisco Vásquez Cuevas"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:39
msgid "Merge multiple PDF files into a single document"
msgstr "Mesti mitu PDF-faili üheks dokumendiks"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:43
msgid "Reorder and remove pages before saving a new PDF"
msgstr ""
"Muuda lehtede järjestust ja eemalda lehti ning salvesta tulemus uue PDF-"
"failina"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:47
msgid "Extract selected pages into a new document"
msgstr "Eralda valitud lehed uueks dokumendiks"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:51
msgid "Split a PDF into multiple documents"
msgstr "Jaga PDF-fail mitmeks dokumendiks"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:55
msgid "Compress PDF files for smaller output"
msgstr "Tihenda ja paki PDF-fail väiksemaks"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:59
msgid "View and edit PDF metadata"
msgstr "Vaata ja muuda PDF-faili metateavet"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:63
msgid "Add a watermark to specific PDF pages"
msgstr "Lisa vesimärk PDF-faili konkreetsetele lehtedele"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:75
#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:96
#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:125
msgid "New"
msgstr "Uus"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:77
msgid "Add support for mobile window sizes"
msgstr "Lisandus nutiseadmete akende tugi"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:79
#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:87
#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:100
#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:108
#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:116
#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:129
msgid "Changes"
msgstr "Muudatused"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:81
msgid "Improve app responsiveness when resizing it"
msgstr "Rakendus reageerib paremini selle suuruse muutmisel"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:89
msgid "Fixed missing icons and previews in some environments"
msgstr "Lisaime puuduolevad ikoonid ja eelvaated mõnede keskkondade puhul"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:90
msgid "Improved touchscreen support"
msgstr "Parandasime puuteekraani tuge"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:98
msgid "Added a Watermark section"
msgstr "Lisasime vesimärkide kasutamise võimaluse"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:102
msgid "Improved feedback when fields need attention"
msgstr "Parandasime teavitusi, kui mõni andmeväli vajab regaarimist"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:110
msgid "Improved icon scalability and shadows"
msgstr "Parandasime ikoonide skaleeritavust ja varjutamist"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:118
msgid "Rename app from Folios to Quire"
msgstr "Muutsime rakenduse nime: Folios on nüüd Quire"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:119
msgid "Modify app icon"
msgstr "Kohendasime rakenduse ikooni"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:127
msgid ""
"Added an undo action for clearing the document list in the merge section"
msgstr ""
"Lisasime võimaluse mestimisvaate dokumentide loendi kustutamist tagasi "
"pöörata"

#: data/com.fvtronics.Quire.metainfo.xml.in:131
msgid "Improved app usability in small windows"
msgstr "Parandasime rakenduse kasutust väikestest akendest"

